ater from gelatine leaves and set aside. Discard soak water."},{"content":"Place coconut sugar into mixing bowl and mill <b>10 sec\/speed 9<b>."},{"content":"Add mango and cream cheese and mix <b>30 sec\/speed 5<b>, with aid of spatula."},{"content":"Add cream and squeezed gelatine leaves and combine <b>40 sec\/speed 5<b> or until gelatine is dissolved."},{"content":"Pour mixture evenly over base in tin and set aside in refrigerator to set (approx. 5 hours)."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Mango coulis"},{"content":"Place coconut sugar into mixing bowl and mill <b>10 sec\/speed 9<b>."},{"content":"Add mango and lemon juice and blend <b>15 sec\/speed 7<b>."},{"content":"Spread mango coulis over cheesecake and place into refrigerator to set for 30 minutes."},{"content":"Garnish with extra finely sliced mango and serve chilled."}],"basicInfo":["medium","20m","6h 35m","12 slices"]}